text1: Your sensors have detected an anomalous planetary signature. For a moment, the ship's log registered the code “Earth”, but the built-in artificial intelligence quickly corrected this by referring to a mismatch in space coordinates. It is not known who or what “put” this object here, but it is certain that it is nothing short of a true space miracle. The similarity to the homeland of mankind is registered as 97.7766..... and the chance of such an event happening is {exact calculation error/insufficient referenced data, extremely small}.
